---
title: Tex-Mex Style Beyond Meat® Skillet Rice with Sweet Bell Peppers and Cheddar Cheese
description: Cheese lovers, this one is for you! Savoury Beyond Meat® is seasoned with our Mexican Seasoning in a hearty rice skillet with ooey-gooey cheddar cheese on top. A bonus delight comes from the deliciously crispy skillet bits at the bottom of the pan. May your cheese pulls be long and your meal time enjoyable!
